OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fslowly dying out but quite a cloudy
OL,7,Fevening in places with some mist
OL,8,Fpossible. Winds strengthening
OL,9,Fovernight and feeling quite muggy and
OL,10,Fwarm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,13,Fweekend, windy and feeling warm,
OL,14,Fsunshine breaking through in most
OL,15,Fareas. Perhaps some showers later in
OL,16,Fthe day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
