OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FRemaining warm on Sunday and Monday
OL,7,Fbut with a freshening breeze, plenty
OL,8,Fof bright weather but scattered
OL,9,Fshowers. Dry and bright with lighter
OL,10,Fwinds on Tuesday.
